This paper is about detecting phishing emails using data mining and text processing techniques, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms for classification, which can be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves text processing techniques such as stemming and ontology, which can be categorized under information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, since the paper deals with cybersecurity, it can also be categorized under cybercrime (cs.CY).
